Title : List of Tomie chapters
Text : {{DISPLAYTITLE:List of ''Tomie'' chapters}}


''[[Tomie]]'' appeared as a [[Serial (literature)|serial]] in the [[List of manga magazines|manga magazine]] ''Monthly Haloween'' from 1987 to 2000. Two volumes were collected into the overarching series {{nihongo|''The Junji Ito Horror Comic Collection''|伊藤潤二恐怖マンガCollection}} as volume 1 and 2 of the series.<ref name="halloween-vol1" /><ref name="halloween-vol2" /> The manga series was released in an [[Anthology|omnibus]] volume in February 2000 titled, {{nihongo|''Tomie Zen''|富江 (全)}}.<ref name="omnibus-original">{{Cite book| title= 富江―The complete comics of Tomie [コミック]| language= Japanese| publisher= Amazon.co.jp | id=  {{ASIN|4257903961|country=jp}} }}</ref> [[ComicsOne]] released both volumes in April 1, 2001, with flipped artwork (read left-to-right).<ref>{{Cite book| title= Tomie, Volume 1| asin= 1588990842 | publisher=[[Amazon.com]] }}</ref><ref>{{Cite book| title= Tomie, Volume 2| asin= 1588990850 | publisher=[[Amazon.com]] }}</ref>

A second series titled {{nihongo|''Atarashī Tomie''|新しい富江|New Tomie}} was serialized in ''Nemuki'' and was collected into a single bound volume titled {{nihongo|''Tomie Again: Tomie Part 3''|富江Again―富江 Part3}} and released on March 2001.<ref name="nemuki-vol3" /> ''Tomie'' was re-released again as part of {{nihongo|The Junji Ito Museum of Horror|伊藤潤二恐怖博物館}} series.<ref name="rerelease-vol1" /><ref name="rerelease-vol2" /> This version was also released in two volumes with the addition of the chapters originally released in ''Tomie Again''. [[Dark Horse Comics]] released this version in its original right-to left format.<ref name="darkhorse-vol1" /><ref name="darkhorse-vol2" />

Asahi Sonorama re-released the manga again in two volumes as part of the {{nihongo|''Junji Ito Masterpiece Collection''|伊藤潤二傑作集|Itō Junji Kessaku-shū}} on January 20, 2011.<ref name="masterpiece-vol1">{{cite web | title= 富江　上| url= http://publications.asahi.com/ecs/detail/?item_id=12263  | language=Japanese| publisher= [[Asahi Sonorama]]| accessdate=2014-05-14}}</ref><ref name="masterpiece-vol2">{{cite web | title= 富江　下| url= http://publications.asahi.com/ecs/detail/?item_id=12264  | language=Japanese| publisher= [[Asahi Sonorama]]| accessdate=2014-05-14}}</ref>

